tv.matchstick.fling

Class ConnectionResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • tv.matchstick.fling.ConnectionResult

  • public final class ConnectionResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Fling connection result. Contains all possible error codes for when an error happens while connecting to a device. These error codes are used by FlingManager.OnConnectionFailedListener.
